#MEM id=postmortem source=/root/yvon/agent-department/COO/diana/skills/marketplace/postmortem/SKILL.md
M|postmortem|name: postmortem
M|postmortem|description: Blameless post-mortem incident analysis with timeline, root cause, and action items. Use after outages, sec incidents, project failures, or any event you want to prevent recurring.
M|postmortem|user-invocable: true
M|postmortem|Conduct a thorough, blameless analysis of an incident to understand what happened and prevent recurrence.
M|postmortem|Work through each section systematically. Focus on systems and processes, not individuals. The goal is learning, not blame.
