M|postmortem|- **Blameless**: "The deploy script didn't validate" not "Alice deployed without checking"
M|postmortem|- **Thorough timeline**: Include everything, even embarrassing delays
M|postmortem|- **Specific actions**: "Add mem alerting" not "Improve monitoring"
M|postmortem|- **Assigned owners**: Unowned actions don't happen
